msgstr "1. 建立 MaxMind 帳號"

msgid ""
"Sign up for a free MaxMind account to access GeoLite2 databases. MaxMind "
"offers both free and commercial IP geolocation databases."
msgstr ""
"註冊一個免費的 MaxMind 帳號以訪問 GeoLite2 數據庫。MaxMind 提供免費和商業 IP "
"地理定位數據庫。"

